text: The Virtual Hackathon will kick-off tomorrow at 10:00am ET.  Dan Middleton has graciously agreed to help kick off the discussion tomorrow morning.  We have a straw-man agenda here (<https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ROq44KpxuelkOp8GpceFNcv8K6XfWdaOnknzBk73OMc/edit>) that lists the various call-in details, some proposed topics, etc.  We expect participation from the Community in identifying interesting topics to work on and identifying leaders to drive forward various efforts.  Much like the other Hackathons, this will be run in unconference format.  Please feel free to add comments and suggestions to the Google doc referenced above.
